{"surahDetails":{"id":87,"arabicName":"الأعلى","banglaName":"সর্বোন্নত","englishName":"The Most High","enTranslatedName":"Al-A'la","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio-surah/128/ar.alafasy/87.mp3","totalAyah":19},"surah":{"id":87,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"سَبِّحِ ٱسۡمَ رَبِّكَ ٱلۡأَعۡلَى","bangl_text":"আপনি আপনার মহান পালনকর্তার নামের পবিত্রতা বর্ণনা করুন","english_text":"Exalt the name of your Lord, the Most High","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5949.mp3","colorText":"سَبِّحِ [h:14437[ٱ]سْمَ رَبِّكَ [h:14438[ٱ]لْأَعْلَى","juz":30,"ruku":529,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"سَبِّحِ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>سْمَ رَبِّكَ <span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لْأَعْلَى <span class=end>١</span>"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"ٱلَّذِي خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","bangl_text":"যিনি সৃষ্টি করেছেন ও সুবিন্যস্ত করেছেন।","english_text":"Who created and proportioned","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5950.mp3","colorText":"ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ","juz":30,"ruku":529,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"ٱلَّذِى خَلَقَ فَسَوَّىٰ <span class=end>٢</span>"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"وَٱلَّذِي قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","bangl_text":"এবং যিনি সুপরিমিত করেছেন ও পথ প্রদর্শন করেছেন","english_text":"And who destined and [then] guided","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5951.mp3","colorText":"وَ[h:9999[ٱ]لَّذِى قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ","juz":30,"ruku":529,"manzil":7,"htmlColorText":"وَ<span class=ham_wasl>ٱ</span>لَّذِى قَدَّرَ فَهَدَىٰ <span class=end>٣</span>"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"وَٱلَّذِيٓ أَخۡرَجَ ٱلۡمَرۡعَىٰ","bangl_text":"এবং যিনি তৃণাদি উৎপন্ন করেছেন","english_text":"And who brings out the pasture","page":591,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/5952.mp3","colorText":"وَ[h:9999[ٱ]لَّذ[o[ِىٓ] أَخْرَجَ [h:14439[ٱ]لْمَرْعَىٰ","juz":